        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (“utpote sanguine Christi lotos et Dei Spiritu regenitos et sanctificatos,” Calovius). According to Osiander, the higher value and blessing of the brotherly greeting is meant to be indicated; but comp. ",
